Marcade Group said it had agreed to buyEurope Craft Imports Inc for a combination of cash and commonstock.    The company said Europe Craft designs, imports anddistributes menswear and sportswear under the Member's Onlybrand name.    The company said Europe Craft had sales of 70 mln dlrs lastyear.    Marcade said this latest deal is part of an ongoingacquisition phase. Reuter&#3;